text: #LeafsForever Jack Campbell went 4-1-1 with a 2.16 GAA & .918 SV% in 6 starts vs Canadiens last regular season (3-4 with a 1.81 GAA .934 SV% in playoffs)

Jack Campbell was outstanding tonight. Big win to start the season.
